<doc id="446960" wikidata="Q7193495" url="?curid=446960" title="Shaba, Kenya">
<text>Shaba is a town in Kenya, situated 260 km to the southeast of Marsabit and 80 km to the north of the Equator. There is a nearby Shaba National Reserve, located east of the Samburu National Reserve.

